| rebound cursor |
Display clear.
rebound := Form fromBits: Display defaultForm bits.
rebound beDisplay.
KernelInstaller rememberObject: rebound named: 'savedDisplay'.
cursor := Cursor fromBits: (Glyphs at: 88) hotspotX: 0 hotspotY: 0.
cursor beCursor.
Cursor moveCursorToX: 12 y: 34.
Cursor showCursor.
KernelInstaller rememberObject: cursor named: 'savedCursor'.
Transcript show: 'DISPLAY CURSOR SAVED'.
Transcript cr.
KernelInstaller saveSnapshot.
